176	- Empty state: Centered illustration with "No cycles logged yet" message, "Tap + to add your first cycle" subtitle
177	- Add history button at bottom (text button, not part of FAB flow)
178	
179	**Data Requirements:**
180	- All `CycleEntry` records from `CycleEntryProvider`
181	- Sorted by `startDate` descending (most recent first)
182	- `startDate`, `endDate`, `cycleLength`, `notes`, `isIrregular` fields
183	
184	**Interactive Elements:**
185	- Long-press entry → edit/delete bottom sheet
186	- Tap entry → detail bottom sheet with full notes view
187	
188	---
189	
190	### Section 3 (Overlay): New Cycle Entry Bottom Sheet
191	
192	**Description:** Form for logging a new cycle start date and optional notes.
193	
194	**Trigger:** Tap FAB `+`
195	
196	**Widget Type:** `showModalBottomSheet` with `SingleChildScrollView`
197	
198	**Layout:** Bottom sheet with 28dp top corner radius, handle bar, max 90% screen height.
199	
200	**Components:**
201	- Handle bar: 40dp wide, 4dp tall, centered, Stone 300 color
202	- Title: "Log Cycle" (`titleLarge`)
203	- Date picker field: "Period Started" label with date display, tap → `showDatePicker`
204	- Length field (optional): "Cycle Length (days)" numeric input, pre-filled with average
205	- Notes field: Multi-line `TextField` with 56dp min height, hint "Add notes..."
206	- Irregular toggle: `Switch` with label "Irregular cycle"
207	- Action buttons: "Cancel" (text) and "Save" (primary pill button)
208	- Form validation: Period date required, must be before today
209	
210	**Data Operations:**
211	- On save: `CycleEntryProvider.addEntry(startDate, endDate?, length, notes, isIrregular)`
212	
213	---
214	
215	### Section 4 (Overlay): Entry Detail/Edit Bottom Sheet
216	
217	**Description:** View, edit, or delete existing cycle entry.
218	
219	**Trigger:** Tap or long-press history item
220	
221	**Components:**
222	- Header: Start date (editable via date picker)
223	- Cycle length display (calculated from start/end dates or manual)
224	- Notes field (editable)
225	- Irregular flag toggle
226	- Delete button: `softCoral` text button, triggers confirmation dialog
227	- "Save Changes" primary button
228	
229	---
230	
231	### Section 5 (Overlay): Ovulation Detail Bottom Sheet
232	
233	**Description:** Explains the ovulation prediction with educational content.
234	
235	**Trigger:** Tap ovulation window row on Current Cycle Card
236	
237	**Components:**
238	- Header: "Ovulation Prediction" with flower/egg icon
239	- Date display: Large centered date
240	- Explanation text: "Based on your cycle history, ovulation is expected around [date]. Your fertile window is [start] - [end]."
241	- Tip: "Track your cycles consistently for more accurate predictions"
242	- Close button
243	
244	---
245	
246	## 8. Data
247	
248	### Entity: CycleEntry
249	
250	| Field | Type | Required | Description |
251	|---|---|---|---|
252	| `id` | `String` (UUID) | Yes | Unique identifier |
253	| `startDate` | `DateTime` | Yes | First day of period |
254	| `endDate` | `DateTime` | No | Last day of period (can be inferred) |
255	| `cycleLength` | `int` | No | Manual override for cycle length |
256	| `notes` | `String` | No | User notes about this cycle |
257	| `isIrregular` | `bool` | No | Flag for irregular patterns |
258	
259	### Provider: CycleEntryProvider
260	
261	**State:**
262	- `entries: List<CycleEntry>` — all logged cycles
263	- `averageCycleLength: int` — calculated from entries (default 28)
264	
265	**Methods:**
266	- `addEntry(entry)` — adds new cycle entry
267	- `updateEntry(id, entry)` — modifies existing entry
268	- `deleteEntry(id)` — removes entry
269	- `getCurrentCycle()` — returns most recent entry
270	- `getOvulationWindow()` — calculates fertile window based on average
271	
272	**Computed:**
273	- `daysSinceLastPeriod` = today - lastPeriodDate
274	- `nextPeriodEstimate` = lastPeriodDate + averageCycleLength
275	
276	---
277	
278	## 9. Motion
279	
280	### Entry Animations
281	
282	- Screen pushes with 300ms slide + fade (standard page transition)
283	- Current Cycle Card: 200ms fade-in on load
284	- History list items: Staggered reveal, 50ms delay between items, 200ms per item fade+slide
285	
286	### Bottom Sheet Animations
287	
288	- FAB → sheet: 250ms smooth deceleration slide-up
289	- Sheet dismiss: 200ms slide-down with fade
290	
291	### Interactive Feedback
292	
293	- History item tap: 200ms scale to 98% with shadow lift
294	- FAB press: 200ms scale to 90%, shadow intensifies
295	- Save button: 200ms scale to 95%
296	
297	### Pull-to-refresh
298	
299	- Not applicable (cycle data doesn't change external to this screen)
300	
301	---
302	
303	## 10. Accessibility
304	
305	### Semantic Labels
306	
307	| Element | Semantic Label |
308	|---|---|
309	| AppBar | `'Cycle Tracking, back button to return to Browse'` |
310	| Current Cycle Card | `'Current cycle, day ${day} since last period, fertile window ${date range}'` |
311	| Days counter | `'${days} days since last period'` |
312	| Ovulation row | `'Tap to learn about your fertile window'` |
313	| FAB | `'Add new cycle entry, double tap to open form'` |
314	| History item | `'Cycle from ${startDate} to ${endDate}, ${length} days${isIrregular ? ', irregular' : ''}'` |
315	
316	### Focus Order
317	
318	1. AppBar back button
319	2. Current Cycle Card (entire card)
320	3. Ovulation window row (focusable for details)
321	4. History list items (in order)
322	5. FAB
323	
324	### Contrast Notes
325	
326	- `lavenderBloom` on white: ~5.2:1 (passes AA)
327	- `deepGraphite` on morningMist: ~12:1 (passes AAA)
328	- `stoneGrey` on white: ~4.7:1 (passes AA for body text)
329	- `blushRose` used at 20% opacity for fertile window background (not text)
330	
331	### Screen Reader Support
332	
333	- Announce cycle logging success: "Cycle entry saved"
334	- Announce deletion: "Cycle entry deleted"
335	- Use `Semantics` to label cycle progress visually
336	
337	### Touch Target Compliance
338	
339	- All interactive elements: 48dp minimum
340	- FAB: 56dp (exceeds minimum)
341	- History items: Full card tap, 56dp+ height
342	- All buttons: 48dp minimum height
343	
344	---
345	
346	## 11. Anti-Patterns
347	
348	**Do Not:**
349	- Use `GridView` for history list (simple `ListView` is appropriate)
350	- Add bottom navigation (per UX spec, BottomNavigationBar is hidden)
351	- Show FAB on initial load with no animation (fade-in over 200ms)
352	- Use hard-coded cycle length (calculate from `CycleEntryProvider`)
353	- Place FAB in bottom center (bottom-right per design system)
354	- Use pure black text on white backgrounds
355	- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito
356	- Add shadows to AppBar (transparent/floating style)
357	- Use `Navigator.push` instead of `context.push` with GoRouter
358	- Skip safe area handling for FAB position
359	- Display empty state without illustration/guidance text
[2026-05-19T00:50:28.433Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_udzne1miaiiy_1","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Spec: Mindfulness — Screen Specification\n2\t\n3\t## 1. Screen Title\n4\t\n5\t**Mindfulness**\n6\t\n7\t---\n8\t\n9\t## 2. Purpose\n10\t\n11\tGuided breathing exercises, light stretching guides, and mindful activity suggestions. This screen provides anxiety-prone mothers with accessible stress relief tools that are gentle, non-clinical, and quick to use.\n12\t\n13\t---\n14\t\n15\t## 3. Route\n16\t\n17\t`/mindfulness`\n18\t\n19\t---\n20\t\n21\t## 4. Widget Name\n22\t\n23\t`MindfulnessScreen`\n24\t\n25\t---\n26\t\n27\t## 5. Design Tokens\n28\t\n29\t### Colors (Light Theme)\n30\t\n31\t| Token | Hex | Usage |\n32\t|---|---|---|\n33\t| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary brand, AppBar, active states |\n34\t| `blushRose` | `#F9A8D4` | Secondary accent, trimester badges |\n35\t| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Success states, completion checkmarks |\n36\t| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n37\t| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n38\t| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text |\n39\t| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions |\n40\t| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Borders, dividers |\n41\t\n42\t### Typography (Nunito)\n43\t\n44\t| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n45\t|---|---|---|---|---|\n46\t| `headlineMedium` | 22sp | 600 | 28sp | Section headers |\n47\t| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Card titles, exercise names |\n48\t| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | 24sp | Body text, descriptions |\n49\t| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Secondary text, metadata |\n50\t| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | 20sp | Button labels |\n51\t| `caption` | 11sp | 500 | 16sp | Badges, timestamps |\n52\t\n53\t### Spacing (8pt base)\n54\t\n55\t| Token | Value |\n56\t|---|---|\n57\t| `xxs` | 4dp |\n58\t| `xs` | 8dp |\n59\t| `sm` | 12dp |\n60\t| `md` | 16dp |\n61\t| `lg` | 24dp |\n62\t\n63\t### Corner Radius\n64\t\n65\t| Token | Value |\n66\t|---|---|\n67\t| `sm` | 8dp (chips) |\n68\t| `lg` | 16dp (standard cards) |\n69\t| `pill` | 999dp (pills, avatars) |\n70\t\n71\t---\n72\t\n73\t## 6. Layout Rules\n74\t\n75\t### Scaffold Structure\n76\t\n77\t- `Scaffold` with standard `AppBar` (no SliverAppBar needed)\n78\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Mindfulness\", back button (48dp touch target), no FAB\n79\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden on this screen\n80\t- Body: `ListView` with 16dp horizontal padding\n81\t\n82\t### AppBar Behavior\n83\t\n84\t- Background: `lavenderTint` (#F5F3FF)\n85\t- Title: \"Mindfulness\" — `headlineSmall` (SemiBold 20sp), `deepGraphite`\n86\t- Leading: `ArrowBackIOS` icon button with 48dp touch target\n87\t- Center title: `centerTitle: true`\n88\t\n89\t### Body Layout\n90\t\n91\t- `ListView` with two major sections\n92\t- Section vertical spacing: 24dp between major sections\n93\t- Card internal padding: 16dp all sides\n94\t- Card gap: 12dp between cards\n95\t- Bottom safe area: respect home indicator\n96\t\n97\t---\n98\t\n99\t## 7. Sections\n100\t\n101\t### Section 1: Breathing Exercises\n102\t\n103\t**Description:** A card list of breathing exercises with name, duration, and difficulty badge. Tapping a card triggers the `overlay:breathing-exercise` full-screen overlay.\n104\t\n105\t**Widget Type:** `Column` containing section header + `ListView.separated` (vertical)\n106\t\n107\t**Layout:**\n108\t- Section header: \"Breathing Exercises\" (`headlineMedium`, left-aligned)\n109\t- List of `BreathingExerciseCard` widgets\n110\t- Cards separated by 12dp spacing\n111\t\n112\t**Components:**\n113\t\n114\tEach `BreathingExerciseCard` contains:\n115\t- Exercise name (`titleMedium`)\n116\t- Duration text (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`) — e.g., \"2 min\"\n117\t- Difficulty badge chip (`caption`) — \"Beginner\", \"Intermediate\", \"Advanced\"\n118\t- Chevron right icon (`stoneGrey`)\n119\t- Card background: `morningMist` with 16dp radius, soft shadow\n120\t- Entire card is tappable (48dp+ touch target)\n121\t\n122\t**Data Requirements:**\n123\t- Static exercise catalog (no provider for MVP)\n124\t- Exercise fields: `id`, `name`, `durationSeconds`, `difficulty`, `description`\n125\t- Difficulty values: \"Beginner\", \"Intermediate\", \"Advanced\"\n126\t\n127\t**Sample Data:**\n128\t\n129\t```dart\n130\t[\n131\t  { id: \"box-breathing\", name: \"Box Breathing\", duration: 240, difficulty: \"Beginner\", description: \"4-4-4-4 pattern for calm\" },\n132\t  { id: \"deep-breathe\", name: \"Deep Breathing\", duration: 180, difficulty: \"Beginner\", description: \"Simple inhale-exhale relaxation\" },\n133\t  { id: \"4-7-8\", name: \"4-7-8 Technique\", duration: 270, difficulty: \"Intermediate\", description: \"Promotes sleep and reduces anxiety\" },\n134\t  { id: \"energizing\", name: \"Energizing Breath\", duration: 120, difficulty: \"Intermediate\", description: \"Quick energizing breaths\" },\n135\t]\n136\t```\n137\t\n138\t**Interactive Elements:**\n139\t- Tap card → triggers overlay route `overlay:breathing-exercise` with exercise ID parameter\n140\t- Card press feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n141\t\n142\t---\n143\t\n144\t### Section 2: Stretching & Self-Care\n145\t\n146\t**Description:** A card list of stretching routines with routine name, trimester suitability, and estimated time. Tapping triggers `overlay:stretching-guide` bottom sheet.\n147\t\n148\t**Widget Type:** `Column` containing section header + `ListView.separated` (vertical)\n149\t\n150\t**Layout:**\n151\t- Section header: \"Stretching & Self-Care\" (`headlineMedium`, left-aligned)\n152\t- List of `StretchingRoutineCard` widgets\n153\t- Cards separated by 12dp spacing\n154\t\n155\t**Components:**\n156\t\n157\tEach `StretchingRoutineCard` contains:\n158\t- Routine name (`titleMedium`)\n159\t- Trimester badge (pill shape, `blushRose` background) — \"All Trimester\", \"1st Tri\", \"2nd Tri\", \"3rd Tri\"\n160\t- Duration text (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`) — e.g., \"10 min\"\n161\t- Chevron right icon (`stoneGrey`)\n162\t- Card background: `morningMist` with 16dp radius, soft shadow\n163\t\n164\t**Data Requirements:**\n165\t- Static routine catalog\n166\t- Routine fields: `id`, `name`, `durationMinutes`, `trimesterSuitability`, `steps`\n167\t\n168\t**Sample Data:**\n169\t\n170\t```dart\n171\t[\n172\t  { id: \"neck-shoulders\", name: \"Neck & Shoulders\", duration: 5, trimester: \"All\", steps: [...] },\n173\t  { id: \"hip-opener\", name: \"Hip Opener\", duration: 10, trimester: \"2nd/3rd\", steps: [...] },\n174\t  { id: \"standing-stretch\", name: \"Standing Stretch\", duration: 8, trimester: \"1st/2nd\", steps: [...] },\n175\t  { id: \"floor-relaxation\", name: \"Floor Relaxation\", duration: 15, trimester: \"All\", steps: [...] },\n176\t]\n177\t```\n178\t\n179\t**Interactive Elements:**\n180\t- Tap card → triggers overlay route `overlay:stretching-guide` with routine ID parameter\n181\t- Card press feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n182\t\n183\t---\n184\t\n185\t## 8. Data\n186\t\n187\t### Entities\n188\t\n189\t**BreathingExercise**\n190\t- `id`: String — unique identifier\n191\t- `name`: String — exercise name\n192\t- `durationSeconds`: int — duration in seconds\n193\t- `difficulty`: String — \"Beginner\" | \"Intermediate\" | \"Advanced\"\n194\t- `description`: String — brief description\n195\t\n196\t**StretchingRoutine**\n197\t- `id`: String — unique identifier\n198\t- `name`: String — routine name\n199\t- `durationMinutes`: int — estimated duration in minutes\n200\t- `trimesterSuitability`: String — \"All\" | \"1st/2nd\" | \"2nd/3rd\" | etc.\n201\t- `steps`: List<String> — step-by-step instructions\n202\t\n203\t### State Management\n204\t\n205\t- `SelfCareCheckStateProvider` — tracks mindfulness completion (for Home checklist integration)\n206\t  - On completing a breathing exercise or stretching routine: mark the item complete in `SelfCareCheckState`\n207\t\n208\t### Provider Dependencies (MVP)\n209\t\n210\t- No provider dependency for exercise/routine data (static catalog)\n211\t- `SelfCareCheckState` integration is optional for MVP\n212\t\n213\t---\n214\t\n215\t## 9. Motion\n216\t\n217\t### Entry Animations\n218\t\n219\t- Screen loads with staggered fade-in for sections: 50ms delay between sections\n220\t- Section headers fade in with 200ms `easeOut`\n221\t- Cards cascade with 50ms stagger delay between each card\n222\t\n223\t### Interactive Feedback\n224\t\n225\t- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%, then 200ms return to 100%\n226\t- Difficulty/trimester chips: no animation (static badges)\n227\t\n228\t### Overlay Transitions\n229\t\n230\t- Breathing exercise overlay: 300ms slide-up with `Curves.easeInOut` (full-screen)\n231\t- Stretching guide overlay: 250ms slide-up with `Curves.easeOut` (bottom sheet)\n232\t\n233\t---\n234\t\n235\t## 10. Accessibility\n236\t\n237\t### Semantic Labels\n238\t\n239\t| Element | Semantic Label |\n240\t|---|---|\n241\t| AppBar | `'Mindfulness screen, go back'` |\n242\t| Breathing card | `'$name breathing exercise, $duration, $difficulty, tap to start'` |\n243\t| Stretching card | `'$name stretching routine, $duration, tap to view guide'` |\n244\t| Difficulty badge | `'$difficulty level'` |\n245\t| Trimester badge | `'$suitability trimester suitability'` |\n246\t\n247\t### Focus Order\n248\t\n249\t1. AppBar (back button)\n250\t2. Breathing exercises section header\n251\t3. Breathing exercise cards (top to bottom)\n252\t4. Stretching section header\n253\t5. Stretching routine cards (top to bottom)\n254\t\n255\t### Contrast Notes\n256\t\n257\t- All text meets WCAG AA contrast (4.5:1 minimum)\n258\t- `deepGraphite` on `morningMist`: ~12:1\n259\t- `stoneGrey` on `morningMist`: ~4.7:1\n260\t\n261\t### Screen Reader Support\n262\t\n263\t- `ExcludeSemantics` on decorative chevron icons\n264\t- Live region when overlay is triggered: \"Opening $name\"\n265\t\n266\t---\n267\t\n268\t## 11. Anti-Patterns\n269\t\n270\t**Do Not:**\n271\t- Add a FAB to this screen (per UX spec, FAB is None)\n272\t- Add `BottomNavigationBar` (hidden per spec)\n273\t- Use platform default colors — all from design system\n274\t- Use any font other than Nunito\n275\t- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text\n276\t- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp\n277\t- Add animations that are abrupt or bouncy — use gentle `easeInOut`\n278\t- Use gradients on cards — flat `morningMist` only\n279\t- Add more than two main sections — keep it focused\n280\t- Use `GridView` — this is a simple vertical list\n281\t\n282\t---\n283\t\n284\t## 12. Critical Files for Implementation\n285\t\n286\t1. **`lib/router/app_router.dart`** — Add GoRoute entry for `/mindfulness` pointing to `MindfulnessScreen`\n287\t\n288\t2. **`lib/theme/app_theme.dart`** — Reference for design tokens (spacing, colors, typography scale)\n289\t\n290\t3. **`lib/screens/pregnancy_progress/pregnancy_progress_screen.dart`** — Reference implementation pattern for a push-screen with `Scaffold`, `AppBar`, `ListView` body, and card-based content\n291\t\n292\t4. **`.stitch/designs/mindfulness/SPEC.md`** — This specification document\n293\t\n294\t5. **`.stitch/screens.json`** — Reference for screen definitions and overlay parent relationships (`mindfulness` → `breathing-exercise`, `stretching-guide`)\n295\t\n296\t---\n297\t\n298\t## 13. Screen Structure\n299\t\n300\t```\n301\tMindfulnessScreen\n302\t├── Scaffold\n303\t│   ├── AppBar (\"Mindfulness\", back button)\n304\t│   └── body: ListView\n305\t│       ├── Section 1: Breathing Exercises\n306\t│       │   └── ListView.separated\n307\t│       │       └── BreathingExerciseCard × N\n308\t│       └── Section 2: Stretching & Self-Care\n309\t│           └── ListView.separated\n310\t│               └── StretchingRoutineCard × N\n311\t```\n312\t\n313\t---\n314\t\n315\t## 14. Route Definition\n316\t\n317\t```dart\n318\tGoRoute(\n319\t  path: '/mindfulness',\n320\t  builder: (context, state) => const MindfulnessScreen(),\n321\t),\n322\t```\n323\t\n324\t---\n325\t\n326\t## 15. Overlay Handling\n327\t\n328\tThe breathing exercise and stretching guide overlays are separate routes (`overlay:breathing-exercise`, `overlay:stretching-guide`). For MVP, these can be implemented as:\n329\t\n330\t- `BreathingExerciseOverlay` (full-screen, pushes over navigation stack)\n331\t- `StretchingGuideSheet` (bottom sheet, uses `showModalBottomSheet`)"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1bac9eb4-3d31-44ee-82a2-f92446a3861e","uuid":"7bb66577-adc6-4982-9328-a58a3a56eabb","timestamp":"2026-05-19T00:50:28.427Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/designs/mindfulness/SPEC.md","content":"# Spec: Mindfulness — Screen Specification\n\n## 1. Screen Title\n\n**Mindfulness**\n\n---\n\n## 2. Purpose\n\nGuided breathing exercises, light stretching guides, and mindful activity suggestions. This screen provides anxiety-prone mothers with accessible stress relief tools that are gentle, non-clinical, and quick to use.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Route\n\n`/mindfulness`\n\n---\n\n## 4. Widget Name\n\n`MindfulnessScreen`\n\n---\n\n## 5. Design Tokens\n\n### Colors (Light Theme)\n\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary brand, AppBar, active states |\n| `blushRose` | `#F9A8D4` | Secondary accent, trimester badges |\n| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Success states, completion checkmarks |\n| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text |\n| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions |\n| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Borders, dividers |\n\n### Typography (Nunito)\n\n| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| `headlineMedium` | 22sp | 600 | 28sp | Section headers |\n| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Card titles, exercise names |\n| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | 24sp | Body text, descriptions |\n| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Secondary text, metadata |\n| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | 20sp | Button labels |\n| `caption` | 11sp | 500 | 16sp | Badges, timestamps |\n\n### Spacing (8pt base)\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `xxs` | 4dp |\n| `xs` | 8dp |\n| `sm` | 12dp |\n| `md` | 16dp |\n| `lg` | 24dp |\n\n### Corner Radius\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `sm` | 8dp (chips) |\n| `lg` | 16dp (standard cards) |\n| `pill` | 999dp (pills, avatars) |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Layout Rules\n\n### Scaffold Structure\n\n- `Scaffold` with standard `AppBar` (no SliverAppBar needed)\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Mindfulness\", back button (48dp touch target), no FAB\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden on this screen\n- Body: `ListView` with 16dp horizontal padding\n\n### AppBar Behavior\n\n- Background: `lavenderTint` (#F5F3FF)\n- Title: \"Mindfulness\" — `headlineSmall` (SemiBold 20sp), `deepGraphite`\n- Leading: `ArrowBackIOS` icon button with 48dp touch target\n- Center title: `centerTitle: true`\n\n### Body Layout\n\n- `ListView` with two major sections\n- Section vertical spacing: 24dp between major sections\n- Card internal padding: 16dp all sides\n- Card gap: 12dp between cards\n- Bottom safe area: respect home indicator\n\n---\n\n## 7. Sections\n\n### Section 1: Breathing Exercises\n\n**Description:** A card list of breathing exercises with name, duration, and difficulty badge. Tapping a card triggers the `overlay:breathing-exercise` full-screen overlay.\n\n**Widget Type:** `Column` containing section header + `ListView.separated` (vertical)\n\n**Layout:**\n- Section header: \"Breathing Exercises\" (`headlineMedium`, left-aligned)\n- List of `BreathingExerciseCard` widgets\n- Cards separated by 12dp spacing\n\n**Components:**\n\nEach `BreathingExerciseCard` contains:\n- Exercise name (`titleMedium`)\n- Duration text (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`) — e.g., \"2 min\"\n- Difficulty badge chip (`caption`) — \"Beginner\", \"Intermediate\", \"Advanced\"\n- Chevron right icon (`stoneGrey`)\n- Card background: `morningMist` with 16dp radius, soft shadow\n- Entire card is tappable (48dp+ touch target)\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- Static exercise catalog (no provider for MVP)\n- Exercise fields: `id`, `name`, `durationSeconds`, `difficulty`, `description`\n- Difficulty values: \"Beginner\", \"Intermediate\", \"Advanced\"\n\n**Sample Data:**\n\n```dart\n[\n  { id: \"box-breathing\", name: \"Box Breathing\", duration: 240, difficulty: \"Beginner\", description: \"4-4-4-4 pattern for calm\" },\n  { id: \"deep-breathe\", name: \"Deep Breathing\", duration: 180, difficulty: \"Beginner\", description: \"Simple inhale-exhale relaxation\" },\n  { id: \"4-7-8\", name: \"4-7-8 Technique\", duration: 270, difficulty: \"Intermediate\", description: \"Promotes sleep and reduces anxiety\" },\n  { id: \"energizing\", name: \"Energizing Breath\", duration: 120, difficulty: \"Intermediate\", description: \"Quick energizing breaths\" },\n]\n```\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap card → triggers overlay route `overlay:breathing-exercise` with exercise ID parameter\n- Card press feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n\n---\n\n### Section 2: Stretching & Self-Care\n\n**Description:** A card list of stretching routines with routine name, trimester suitability, and estimated time. Tapping triggers `overlay:stretching-guide` bottom sheet.\n\n**Widget Type:** `Column` containing section header + `ListView.separated` (vertical)\n\n**Layout:**\n- Section header: \"Stretching & Self-Care\" (`headlineMedium`, left-aligned)\n- List of `StretchingRoutineCard` widgets\n- Cards separated by 12dp spacing\n\n**Components:**\n\nEach `StretchingRoutineCard` contains:\n- Routine name (`titleMedium`)\n- Trimester badge (pill shape, `blushRose` background) — \"All Trimester\", \"1st Tri\", \"2nd Tri\", \"3rd Tri\"\n- Duration text (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`) — e.g., \"10 min\"\n- Chevron right icon (`stoneGrey`)\n- Card background: `morningMist` with 16dp radius, soft shadow\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- Static routine catalog\n- Routine fields: `id`, `name`, `durationMinutes`, `trimesterSuitability`, `steps`\n\n**Sample Data:**\n\n```dart\n[\n  { id: \"neck-shoulders\", name: \"Neck & Shoulders\", duration: 5, trimester: \"All\", steps: [...] },\n  { id: \"hip-opener\", name: \"Hip Opener\", duration: 10, trimester: \"2nd/3rd\", steps: [...] },\n  { id: \"standing-stretch\", name: \"Standing Stretch\", duration: 8, trimester: \"1st/2nd\", steps: [...] },\n  { id: \"floor-relaxation\", name: \"Floor Relaxation\", duration: 15, trimester: \"All\", steps: [...] },\n]\n```\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap card → triggers overlay route `overlay:stretching-guide` with routine ID parameter\n- Card press feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n\n---\n\n## 8. Data\n\n### Entities\n\n**BreathingExercise**\n- `id`: String — unique identifier\n- `name`: String — exercise name\n- `durationSeconds`: int — duration in seconds\n- `difficulty`: String — \"Beginner\" | \"Intermediate\" | \"Advanced\"\n- `description`: String — brief description\n\n**StretchingRoutine**\n- `id`: String — unique identifier\n- `name`: String — routine name\n- `durationMinutes`: int — estimated duration in minutes\n- `trimesterSuitability`: String — \"All\" | \"1st/2nd\" | \"2nd/3rd\" | etc.\n- `steps`: List<String> — step-by-step instructions\n\n### State Management\n\n- `SelfCareCheckStateProvider` — tracks mindfulness completion (for Home checklist integration)\n  - On completing a breathing exercise or stretching routine: mark the item complete in `SelfCareCheckState`\n\n### Provider Dependencies (MVP)\n\n- No provider dependency for exercise/routine data (static catalog)\n- `SelfCareCheckState` integration is optional for MVP\n\n---\n\n## 9. Motion\n\n### Entry Animations\n\n- Screen loads with staggered fade-in for sections: 50ms delay between sections\n- Section headers fade in with 200ms `easeOut`\n- Cards cascade with 50ms stagger delay between each card\n\n### Interactive Feedback\n\n- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%, then 200ms return to 100%\n- Difficulty/trimester chips: no animation (static badges)\n\n### Overlay Transitions\n\n- Breathing exercise overlay: 300ms slide-up with `Curves.easeInOut` (full-screen)\n- Stretching guide overlay: 250ms slide-up with `Curves.easeOut` (bottom sheet)\n\n---\n\n## 10. Accessibility\n\n### Semantic Labels\n\n| Element | Semantic Label |\n|---|---|\n| AppBar | `'Mindfulness screen, go back'` |\n| Breathing card | `'$name breathing exercise, $duration, $difficulty, tap to start'` |\n| Stretching card | `'$name stretching routine, $duration, tap to view guide'` |\n| Difficulty badge | `'$difficulty level'` |\n| Trimester badge | `'$suitability trimester suitability'` |\n\n### Focus Order\n\n1. AppBar (back button)\n2. Breathing exercises section header\n3. Breathing exercise cards (top to bottom)\n4. Stretching section header\n5. Stretching routine cards (top to bottom)\n\n### Contrast Notes\n\n- All text meets WCAG AA contrast (4.5:1 minimum)\n- `deepGraphite` on `morningMist`: ~12:1\n- `stoneGrey` on `morningMist`: ~4.7:1\n\n### Screen Reader Support\n\n- `ExcludeSemantics` on decorative chevron icons\n- Live region when overlay is triggered: \"Opening $name\"\n\n---\n\n## 11. Anti-Patterns\n\n**Do Not:**\n- Add a FAB to this screen (per UX spec, FAB is None)\n- Add `BottomNavigationBar` (hidden per spec)\n- Use platform default colors — all from design system\n- Use any font other than Nunito\n- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text\n- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp\n- Add animations that are abrupt or bouncy — use gentle `easeInOut`\n- Use gradients on cards — flat `morningMist` only\n- Add more than two main sections — keep it focused\n- Use `GridView` — this is a simple vertical list\n\n---\n\n## 12. Critical Files for Implementation\n\n1. **`lib/router/app_router.dart`** — Add GoRoute entry for `/mindfulness` pointing to `MindfulnessScreen`\n\n2. **`lib/theme/app_theme.dart`** — Reference for design tokens (spacing, colors, typography scale)\n\n3. **`lib/screens/pregnancy_progress/pregnancy_progress_screen.dart`** — Reference implementation pattern for a push-screen with `Scaffold`, `AppBar`, `ListView` body, and card-based content\n\n4. **`.stitch/designs/mindfulness/SPEC.md`** — This specification document\n\n5. **`.stitch/screens.json`** — Reference for screen definitions and overlay parent relationships (`mindfulness` → `breathing-exercise`, `stretching-guide`)\n\n---\n\n## 13. Screen Structure\n\n```\nMindfulnessScreen\n├── Scaffold\n│   ├── AppBar (\"Mindfulness\", back button)\n│   └── body: ListView\n│       ├── Section 1: Breathing Exercises\n│       │   └── ListView.separated\n│       │       └── BreathingExerciseCard × N\n│       └── Section 2: Stretching & Self-Care\n│           └── ListView.separated\n│               └── StretchingRoutineCard × N\n```\n\n---\n\n## 14. Route Definition\n\n```dart\nGoRoute(\n  path: '/mindfulness',\n  builder: (context, state) => const MindfulnessScreen(),\n),\n```\n\n---\n\n## 15. Overlay Handling\n\nThe breathing exercise and stretching guide overlays are separate routes (`overlay:breathing-exercise`, `overlay:stretching-guide`). For MVP, these can be implemented as:\n\n- `BreathingExerciseOverlay` (full-screen, pushes over navigation stack)\n- `StretchingGuideSheet` (bottom sheet, uses `showModalBottomSheet`)","numLines":331,"startLine":1,"totalLines":331}}}
