eaders, subtitles, body text, and captions. Color palette centers on lavender bloom as the primary shade, with lavender tint as the scaffold background, blush rose for secondary accents, soft mint for tertiary elements, and morning for additional tonal variations. - Secondary text uses stone grey (#6B7280), with misty borders in (#E5E7EB), soft coral for errors (#EF4444), and warm white (#FFFFFF) for bottom navigation. Dark mode shifts to twilight bloom (#9F67FF) as the primary, dusky rose (#FBC4E0) for secondary accents, night mint (#34D399) for tertiary elements, deep twilight (#1E1B2E) for cards, and night sky (#13111C) for the scaffold background.\n\nMotion throughout the interface follows a gentle, purposeful approach. Page transitions take 300ms, micro-interactions are snappy at 200ms, and hero animations span 350ms with staggered list reveals occurring every 50ms between items.\n\nThe design prevents common issues by enforcing strict constraints: no platform defaults, custom text sizing, or inconsistent spacing. Shadows must serve a hierarchy purpose, and the font choice is locked to Nunito. No gradients, generic gradients, or desktop patterns allowed. Touch targets need to be at least 48dp, critical actions must stay in the thumb zone, and pure black or white cannot be used in the color system.\n","signature":"b155671f17c07b2a829d6fca7d40c862a2aa9d6fc7136d0c4efcc6a191ac981f"}],"model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":44798,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0},"service_tier":"standard","context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1bac9eb4-3d31-44ee-82a2-f92446a3861e","uuid":"0e2acdec-bd12-44e2-aa80-62d24bdb71b8"}
